<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="4" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="5.[113,772,1618,1834]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">
DISTRIBUTION. 
<collectingCountry box="[278,503,1650,1674]" name="Dominican Republic" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Dominican Republic</collectingCountry>
(Hispaniola Island) and Mona Island (
<collectingCountry box="[264,399,1682,1706]" name="Puerto Rico" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Puerto Rico</collectingCountry>
). This species was described from Mona Island as 
<taxonomicName authority="Santiago-Blay, 2009" authorityName="Santiago-Blay" authorityYear="2009" box="[312,767,1714,1738]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Rhopalurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virkkii">
<emphasis box="[312,521,1714,1738]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Rhopalurus virkkii</emphasis>
Santiago-Blay, 2009
</taxonomicName>
, but 
<bibRefCitation author="ESPOSITO" box="[157,393,1746,1770]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" pagination="1 - 134" refId="ref4077" refString="ESPOSITO, L. A., H. Y. YAMAGUTI, C. A. DE SOUZA, R. PINTO-DA-ROCHA &amp; L. PRENDINI. 2017. Systematic revision of the Neotropical club-tailed scorpions, Physoctonus, Rhopalurus, and Troglorhopalurus, revalidation of Heteroctenus, and descriptions of two new genera and three new species (Buthidae: Rhopalurusinae). Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History, 415: 1 - 134." type="journal article" year="2017">Esposito et al. (2017)</bibRefCitation>
transferred it to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pocock" authorityYear="1893" box="[582,723,1747,1770]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Heteroctenus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[582,723,1747,1770]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Heteroctenus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and synonymized it with 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Armas &amp; Marcano Fondeur" baseAuthorityYear="1987" box="[353,451,1778,1802]" class="Arachnida" family="Buthidae" genus="Heteroctenus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Scorpiones" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abudi">
<emphasis box="[353,451,1778,1802]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">H. abudi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as previously suggested by Teruel &amp; Armas (2012: 216-217).
</paragraph>
